messages.content: Thank you for calling Google customer service! My name is Davinci. May I know your name, please?
Hi Davinci, my name is Julia.
Hello Julia, nice to meet you! How can I assist you today?
I have a few questions about your Gmail service.
Of course! What specifically would you like to know about Gmail?
I am curious about the storage capacity and how to manage it effectively.

Great question! Gmail offers 15 GB of free storage shared across Google Drive, Gmail, and Google Photos. You can manage your storage by deleting unnecessary emails, especially those with large attachments, and by using Google Drive to store larger files.
That sounds useful. Is there a way to check how much storage I have used?
Yes, Julia. You can check your storage usage by going to the Google One website or the storage section in your Google account settings. It provides a detailed breakdown of your usage.
Thanks for the information, Davinci. This has been really helpful.
You're welcome, Julia! I'm glad I could help. If you have any more questions or need further assistance, feel free to ask.
I think that's all I needed for now. Have a great day!
You too, Julia! Thank you for contacting Google customer service. Goodbye!
